V<p>I&#8217;ve had an overwhelming response to yesterday&#8217;s post about getting your help in translating my comics. In less than 24 hours I&#8217;ve received nearly 500 emails! I was expecting to get like 20 or 30 emails, but 500? I&#8217;m incredibly touched and flattered by your response and generosity. From the bottom of my heart \u2026 THANK YOU! Can I kindly ask that you stop sending emails as I think I should have more than enough volunteers for now.</p>\u000a<p>Next is the task of sorting through all the emails and organising this project properly. For each language I&#8217;ll be picking about 10 people, dividing the comics up between them and sending them a handful of &#8216;blank&#8217; comics with the text removed. They will have to place the translated copy on themselves (I will provide some fonts) so some knowledge of layout software is required. I won&#8217;t be able to respond to each of your emails individually so If you don&#8217;t hear from me please don&#8217;t be offended, and thank you again for offering to help.</p>\u000a<p>The response from my readers continues to amaze me.<br />\u000a- Gav</p>
